469
00:34:56,980 --> 00:34:59,190
"Sometimes treating,

470
00:34:59,190 --> 00:35:02,890
often helping, always comforting".

471
00:35:05,330 --> 00:35:07,780
Right now I don't want to tell you

472
00:35:07,780 --> 00:35:12,230
